<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Great News About Your {{year}} {{make}} {{model}}</title>
</head>
<body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f4f4f4; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;">
  <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #f4f4f4;">
    <tr>
      <td align="center" style="padding: 20px 0;">
        <table role="presentation" width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);">

          <!-- Header -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background-color: {{brandPrimaryColor}}; padding: 30px 40px; text-align: center;">
              {{#if dealershipLogo}}
              <img src="{{dealershipLogo}}" alt="{{dealershipName}}" style="max-height: 60px; margin-bottom: 10px;">
              {{else}}
              <h2 style="color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 24px;">{{dealershipName}}</h2>
              {{/if}}
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Hero Banner -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background-color: {{brandSecondaryColor}}; padding: 25px 40px; text-align: center;">
              <h1 style="color: #ffffff; margin: 0; font-size: 28px; line-height: 1.3;">Great News, {{firstName}}!</h1>
              <p style="color: #ffffff; margin: 10px 0 0; font-size: 16px; opacity: 0.9;">Your vehicle is worth more than you owe.</p>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Main Content -->
          <tr>
            <td style="padding: 40px;">
              <p style="color: #333333; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 20px;">
                Dear {{firstName}} {{lastName}},
              </p>
              <p style="color: #333333; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 20px;">
                Great news! Your <strong>{{year}} {{make}} {{model}} {{trim}}</strong> is worth more than you owe! That means you have positive equity that can be applied toward your next vehicle.
              </p>

              <!-- Equity Highlight Box -->
              <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 25px 0;">
                <tr>
                  <td style="background-color: #f0faf0; border: 2px solid #2e7d32; border-radius: 8px; padding: 25px; text-align: center;">
                    <p style="color: #555555; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 5px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;">Your Estimated Equity</p>
                    <p style="color: #2e7d32; font-size: 42px; font-weight: bold; margin: 0;">{{equityAmount}}</p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <!-- Offer Details -->
              <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin: 25px 0;">
                <tr>
                  <td width="50%" style="padding: 15px; background-color: #fafafa; border-radius: 8px 0 0 8px; text-align: center; border-right: 1px solid #eeeeee;">
                    <p style="color: #888888; font-size: 12px; margin: 0 0 5px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;">Trade-In Offer</p>
                    <p style="color: #333333; font-size: 26px; font-weight: bold; margin: 0;">{{offerAmount}}</p>
                  </td>
                  <td width="50%" style="padding: 15px; background-color: #fafafa; border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0; text-align: center;">
                    <p style="color: #888888; font-size: 12px; margin: 0 0 5px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px;">Monthly Savings Potential</p>
                    <p style="color: #333333; font-size: 26px; font-weight: bold; margin: 0;">{{monthlySavings}}</p>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>

              <p style="color: #333333; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 20px;">
                With today's strong demand for pre-owned vehicles like yours, now is an excellent time to take advantage of your equity. You could lower your monthly payment, upgrade to a newer model, or both.
              </p>

              <p style="color: #333333; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 30px;">
                This offer is based on current market conditions and your vehicle's history. Values can change, so we encourage you to act soon.
              </p>

              <!-- CTA Button -->
              <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">
                <tr>
                  <td align="center">
                    <a href="{{dealershipWebsite}}" style="display: inline-block; background-color: {{brandPrimaryColor}}; color: #ffffff; font-size: 18px; font-weight: bold; text-decoration: none; padding: 15px 40px; border-radius: 6px;">
                      Explore Your Options
                    </a>
                  </td>
                </tr>
              </table>
            </td>
          </tr>

          <!-- Footer -->
          <tr>
            <td style="background-color: #333333; padding: 30px 40px; text-align: center;">
              <p style="color: #ffffff; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; margin: 0 0 5px;">{{dealershipName}}</p>
              <p style="color: #aaaaaa; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 5px;">
                <a href="tel:{{dealershipPhone}}" style="color: #aaaaaa; text-decoration: none;">{{dealershipPhone}}</a>
              </p>
              <p style="color: #aaaaaa; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 15px;">
                <a href="{{dealershipWebsite}}" style="color: #aaaaaa; text-decoration: none;">{{dealershipWebsite}}</a>
              </p>
              <p style="color: #777777; font-size: 11px; margin: 0; line-height: 1.5;">
                This offer is an estimate based on current market data and is subject to in-person vehicle inspection.
                If you no longer wish to receive these emails, please contact us to opt out.
              </p>
            </td>
          </tr>

        </table>
      </td>
    </tr>
  </table>
</body>
</html>
